context: so the wall was, did it say finished? Isn't that good? The wall was finished in the twenty and fifth day of the month, Elul. Notice what it says, in fifty and two days.

and it came to pass that when all our enemies heard thereof, and all the heathen that were about us saw these things, they were much cast down in their own eyes. Notice what it says, for they perceived that this work was wrought of our God.
